snippet.title: Ellen Degeneres Explains Why She’s Ending Her Show
snippet.description:
Ellen DeGeneres announced yesterday that she will end her talk show after next season. Savannah Guthrie speaks with DeGeneres about the decision, which comes 10 months after DeGeneres faced accusations of allowing/running a toxic workplace.
